OL,3,CParents of terror attack victim recall
OL,4,Cmoment they were told of son's murder
OL,6,FThe parents of James Furlong have
OL,7,Fspoken of the heartbreaking moment
OL,8,Fthey found out their son had been
OL,9,Fkilled in a terrorist attack in
OL,10,FReading.
OL,12,FGary and Jan Furlong say they spoke to
OL,13,Ftheir son, on the telephone, on the
OL,14,Fmorning on June 20, 2020.
OL,16,FAs it was a sunny day and lockdown
OL,17,Frestrictions had been lifted, James
OL,18,Ftold his parents he might meet up with
OL,19,Fsome friends in Forbury Gardens later
OL,20,Fin the day.
