OL,6,FThe couple then said their goodbyes to
OL,7,Ftheir son, not knowing that would be
OL,8,Fthe last time they would speak to him.
OL,10,FThat evening, Gary and Jan were at
OL,11,Ftheir home in Liverpool when the news
OL,12,Fbroke that an incident had occurred in
OL,13,FForbury Gardens, Reading.
OL,15,FThey called their son on his mobile
OL,16,Fphone several times but could not get
OL,17,Fhold of him.
