OL,3,CParents of terror attack victim recall
OL,4,Cmoment they were told of son's murder
OL,6,FGary said: "I felt genuinely sorry for
OL,7,Fthe policeman because he had to come
OL,8,Fin and tell us. He told me in the
OL,9,Fhallway and Jan collapsed in the back
OL,10,Fkitchen, it was mayhem.
OL,12,F"It took us another five days to go
OL,13,Fand see James.
OL,15,F"The hardest thing we done was to go
OL,16,Fback to his flat to find plates and
OL,17,Fdifferent things where he'd just ate a
OL,18,Fsandwich before he'd gone out.
OL,20,F"That was heartbreaking."
