OL,6,FJames, who is described by his parents
OL,7,Fas a "kind and gentle man" was Head of
OL,8,FHistory, Government and Politics at
OL,9,FThe Holt School, Wokingham.
OL,11,FFollowing his death, a mosaic memorial
OL,12,Fwas unveiled at the school in James'
OL,13,Fmemory.
OL,15,FGary and Jan received hundreds of
OL,16,Fletters and cards from pupils at The
OL,17,FHolt in the days and weeks after the
OL,18,Fattack.
