OL,3,CParents of terror attack victim recall
OL,4,Cmoment they were told of son's murder
OL,6,FJan said: "You never forget an amazing
OL,7,Fteacher do you? He was so kind and
OL,8,Fwhat the children said about him,
OL,9,Fthat's his legacy for them children.
OL,11,F"I think of all them young girls,
OL,12,Fthey've probably left school now, and
OL,13,FI just think how he inspired them all
OL,14,Fgoing on in life and they'll never
OL,15,Fforget him."
OL,17,FGary said: "He was the happiest he
OL,18,Fever was at the school. When we go
OL,19,Fback and visit the school, that's
OL,20,FJames, we feel James there.
