OL,3,CParents of terror attack victim recall
OL,4,Cmoment they were told of son's murder
OL,6,F"We miss him so much. Mine and Jan's
OL,7,Flives will never, ever be the same
OL,8,Fagain. We're not the same people we
OL,9,Fwere before 7pm on Saturday the 20th
OL,10,Fof June, 2020."
